snippet.title: Amber Rose Trashes Women From Philly | TMZ Live
snippet.description:
Amber Rose was on the 'Drink Champs' podcast when she said women from Philly are not traditionally pretty and we spoke with Torrei Hart who is also from Philly to get her take on Amber’s offensive comments.
